@end lisp

Here the awkwardness of Common Lisp masks the basic elegance of the idea,
which would be more visible in Scheme:

@lisp
((! remove-if) oddp lst)


     (defun memoize (fn)
       (let ((cache (make-hash-table :test #'equal)))
          #'(lambda (&rest args)
